// PATCH(greptile-3): AuthHeader no longer overwrites AuthSource. Load() is the
// only place AuthSource gets labeled (env vs config). When the token came from
// disk, AuthHeader would previously mislabel it as "env:SURGEGRAPH_TOKEN",
// causing doctor to misreport the auth source after `auth login`.
// Also: prefer AccessToken (OAuth) over SurgegraphToken (static) when both are
// present and OAuth was the most recent path — but in normal use only one of
// the two fields is populated, so the precedence order below is what matters
// for static-token users.
